<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="illegal-adj">illegal <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪ'liːɡl/    美 /ɪ'liːɡl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>不合法的；违法的：</strong></h4>
<p>反 legal </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Wild camping is illegal in England.
在英国，野外露营是违法的。</p><footer>2018 江苏</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>illegal activities</strong>
违法活动</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>It's illegal to drive</strong> a car without a driver's license.
无照驾车是违法的。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>illegally /ɪ'liːɡəli/ adv   </p></div>